- 'Average team fantasy points' is the average of fantasy points scored by all players in a team;
- 'Total salary' is the sum of salaries of all players in a team.

- 'stands out like a beacon' refers to the team with the highest rating;
- 'shining the brightest' refers to the team with the maximum rating;
- 'overall performance' is calculated as the total fantasy points divided by the average fantasy points of the positions;
